  <h2 class="android-font android-slogan">Full-Stack Developer</h2>
  <p class="android-sub-slogan">Sou do Rio de Janeiro, moro em São Paulo e sou <i>CTO</i>
    da <a class="android-link" href="https://www.ingresse.com/" target="_blank">Ingresse</a>.
  </p>

  <a href="#talks">
    <button class="android-fab mdl-button mdl-button--colored mdl-js-button mdl-button--fab mdl-js-ripple-effect">
      <i class="material-icons">expand_more</i>
    </button>
